    "It emphasizes contemporary reinterpretations of traditional Christian virtues, focusing on personal moral development, social justice, environmental stewardship, and inclusivity.",
    "Similarly, the outputs reflect a social perspective that aligns with contemporary progressive social values, emphasizing collective responsibilities towards environmental stewardship and social justice, advocating for responsible and ethical communication, and highlighting the importance of economic equity.",
